Class FriendRequestModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.chinesecheckers.models.FriendRequestModel
  • public class FriendRequestModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Models friend requests and the data it contains. It shows who created the friend request, the target user, and if it has been accepted.
